quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  29,15,"Men da…óndi Nuuhu yooloragol halakuyee, e gom…óim…ìe wondunoo…ìe e makko …ìen ka laana; Men wa…ói laana kan, waajitorka yim…ìe …ìen."
  29,16,"An Nulaa…óo, janto kadi fillayee Ibraahiima on, nde o wi'annoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: rewee Alla tun, huliron lepte Makko …óen, …óoftagol yamirooje Makko …óen, wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin; ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, si wonii hi…óon anndi."
  29,17,"Anndee ko rewoton kon, onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, ko sanamuuji …ói nafataa …ói loraataa, hi…óon ta∆¥a fenaande, aa∆¥agol wonnde hi…ói hanndi e reweede. Pellet, …óin …ói rewoton gaani Alla, …ói waawaa on arsikude, sakko …ói wa…óa …óum; awa …óa…ì…ìiree arsike on ka Alla, tawde ko Kanko woni arsikoowo On, rewon Mo Kanko tun, yettiron Mo neema arsike on. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon, √ëalnde Darngal, fii hasbeede yo…ìitee, wanaa ka sanamuuji mon."
  29,18,"Si onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe on fennii ko Muhammadu (jom kisiyee) addi kon, haray mofte adinoo…ìe on kadi feenniino Nuuhu e 'Adi e Samuuda e wo…ó…ìe goo. Alaa ko fawii e Nulaa…óo on, si wanaa yottingol …ìanngina. Gom…óii le o yottinii e mo'on, ko Joomi makko nuli mo e mon kon."
  29,19,"E …ìee fennoo…ìe yi'aali no Alla fu…ó…óorta non tagu ngun, refti O ruttitay ngu …ìaawo fii maggu gasude? Pellet, …óum ko ko newanii Alla. Ko O hattan…óo, Mo huunde ronkintaa Mbo."
  29,20,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee fennu…ìe ummital: yiilee ka leydi, tasko…óon no Alla fu…ó…óori tagu ngun. Refti Alla wuurnitay yim…ìe …ìen, e nguurndam goo, fii hasbeede. Pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde. Huunde ronkintaa Mo. Wanaa wuurnitugol yim…ìe …ìen, wano woniri non, O ronkaano tagugol …ìe ka arannde."
  29,21,"Himo leptira nun…óal Makko ngal, mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, O yurminira …ìural Makko ngal, mo O muuyani e ma…ì…ìe. Ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon, √ëalnde Darngal, fii hasbeede, …ìaawo immitineede e genaale mon."
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotoo…ìe Joomi mon, wanaa …ìoccittoo…ìe lepte Makko …óen ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on kadi, gaanin Alla gi…óo heftoowo fii mon, wanaa ballo du√±anay…óo on lepte Makko …óen."
  29,23,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Alla …óen, e hawroygol e Makko ngol √ëalnde Darngal, …ìen ta∆¥ike e yurmeende Am, tawde …ìe naatataa Aljanna poomaa, sabu keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun. ∆Åen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe, ha…ì…ìitii…óe …ìe ka laakara."